Brief Overview

Celebrate the New Year like never before with Nomadic Nights on 31st December and 1st January at Athah Resort, Rishikesh! Dance to electrifying DJ beats, enjoy live music by a cozy bonfire, and marvel at stunning fireworks. Indulge in a celebratory cake and dive into thrilling adventure activities, all in the serene beauty of Rishikesh. This isn’t just a party; it’s an experience to remember. Gather your squad and make this New Year truly unforgettable! 🎉

Event Highlights

Ignite the Night

Cozy up by the crackling bonfire and soak in the magic of a night filled with warmth, stories, and laughter. Watch the flames dance as you relax under the open sky. It’s the perfect blend of chill vibes and glowing memories! 🔥🌌

Rave by the River

Get ready to groove like never before! Dance the night away to electrifying beats under the starlit skies by the riverside. It’s time to let loose, feel the rhythm, and turn the vibe up a notch. This is your ultimate party playground! 🎶✨

Feast Under the Stars

Savor a sumptuous dinner amidst the enchanting outdoors. With gourmet delights and magical starlight above, every bite feels like a celebration. Gather your favorite people and indulge in a culinary experience as extraordinary as the night itself! 🍽️🌠

Cosmic Celebration

Light up your New Year with a dazzling firework display that’ll leave you in awe. Watch the skies come alive with sparkling colors and cosmic bursts. This is your moment to toast to new beginnings and unforgettable nights! 🎇🎆

Delhi
Rishikesh

DAY 1 :Depart from Delhi and Arrival in Rishikesh

  • 3:00 PM – 4:00 PM: Check-in & Welcome

    Arrive at Athah Resort, settle in, and soak in the serene surroundings.

    Meet your fellow travelers and kickstart the fun with engaging games and activities.

  • 5:00 PM – 6:00 PM: Evening Snacks

    Enjoy delicious refreshments as you gear up for an unforgettable evening.

  • 8:00 PM – 12:00 AM: Rave by the River & Gala Dinner

    Dance to electrifying beats, feast on a gourmet dinner, and soak in the festive vibes.

  • 12:00 AM: Cosmic Celebration & Cake Cutting

    Ring in the New Year with dazzling fireworks and a celebratory cake.

    • DAY 2 : Adventure & Entertainment

  • 8:00 AM – 9:30 AM: Breakfast

    Start your day with a hearty breakfast to fuel up for the adventures ahead.

  • 9:30 AM – 1:00 PM: Adventure Activities

  • 1:00 PM – 2:30 PM: Lunch

    Relish a scrumptious lunch to recharge for the second half of the day.

  • 2:30 PM – 5:00 PM: River Crossing & Exploration

    Experience the beauty of Rishikesh as you cross the river and explore the stunning surroundings.

  • 5:00 PM – 6:00 PM: Evening Snacks

    Refuel with tasty snacks before the night’s entertainment begins.

  • 7:00 PM – 10:00 PM: Live Music & Karaoke

    Unwind with soulful live music and let loose on the mic with fun karaoke sessions.

    • DAY 3 : Check-out

    Enjoy a fresh, energizing breakfast before packing up and preparing for departure.

    Take some time to unwind, relax, or explore the resort one last time before check-out.

  • 11:00 AM – 12:00 PM: Check-out

    Pack your bags and check out, carrying with you unforgettable memories from the event.

    • How to reach

    To Delhi

  • By Air: The nearest airport in Delhi is Indira Gandhi International Airport (DEL). Although Rishikesh does not have its own airport, you can take a flight to Jolly Grant Airport (DED) in Dehradun, which is the nearest airport to Rishikesh. The flight duration from Delhi is approximately 1 hour. From Jolly Grant Airport, hire a taxi or take a bus to Rishikesh, which is about 20 km away and takes approximately 30-40 minutes to reach.
  • By Rail: Major railway stations in Delhi include New Delhi Railway Station (NDLS), Old Delhi Railway Station (DLI), and Hazrat Nizamuddin Railway Station (NZM). Take a train to Haridwar Railway Station, which is the nearest major railhead to Rishikesh. Popular trains include the Shatabdi Express, Mussoorie Express, and Jan Shatabdi Express. The train journey takes approximately 4-5 hours. From Haridwar, you can hire a taxi or take a bus to Rishikesh, which is about 20 km away and takes 30-40 minutes.
  • By Road:

    Major bus terminals in Delhi are:

    • Kashmere Gate ISBT
    • Anand Vihar ISBT
    • Sarai Kale Khan ISBT

    Buses, taxis, and private vehicles are available from Delhi to Rishikesh. The distance is approximately 240 km, and the journey takes around 5-6 hours, depending on traffic and road conditions. Overnight and day buses, including AC and Volvo services, are available for a comfortable journey.

    • To Rishikesh

  • By Air

    If you arrive in Rishikesh by air, the nearest airport is Jolly Grant Airport in Dehradun, approximately 20 kilometers away. From Rishikesh, you can take a taxi or a rickshaw to Athah Resort in Taliyal Gaon. The resort is a short 10-15 minute drive from the main town.

  • By Rail

    If you reach Rishikesh by rail, either through Haridwar Junction (25 kilometers away) or Rishikesh Railway Station, the journey to Athah Resort is straightforward. From the railway station, you can hire a taxi or a rickshaw, and it will take approximately 15-20 minutes to reach the resort in Taliyal Gaon.

  • By Road

    If you arrive in Rishikesh by road, Athah Resort in Taliyal Gaon is easily accessible. Once you reach Rishikesh town, you can hire a taxi or a rickshaw to travel to the resort. The journey takes around 10-15 minutes from the town center, depending on traffic conditions.
